### Polars example (Python)


::: {.cell}

```{.python .cell-code}
import polars as pl
from great_tables import GT

(
  pl.read_csv(
    'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jcoliver/learn-r/gh-pages/data/otter-mandible-data.csv',
    null_values='NA'
  )
  .melt(id_vars=['species', 'museum', 'accession'])
  .head()
  .pipe(lambda df_: GT(df_))
)
```

